    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国通货膨胀在Reeves和削减速度的惊喜福音中冷却</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/uk-inflation-unexpectedly-slows-in-boost-for-rate-cut-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国通货膨胀意外冷却，加强了英格兰银行在五月再次降低利率的案件，并在周三的重要经济声明之前为富裕人雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）的总理提供了士气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/uk-inflation-unexpectedly-slows-in-boost-for-rate-cut-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 07:04:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着国家银行发放巨额股息，印尼股票上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/indonesian-stocks-rise-after-mandiri-s-dividend-beats-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在最大的国有银行高于预期的股息支出后，印尼股票在三周内最多，有助于将投资者带回人们对总统政策的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/indonesian-stocks-rise-after-mandiri-s-dividend-beats-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 03:12:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国石油，环境集团在法庭上有争议的天然气允许</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/uk-oil-gas-licenses-challenged-in-court-by-environmental-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个保护小组正在向英国政府挑战伦敦法院，超过31个北海石油和天然气勘探许可证，其说可能会使海洋保护区和气候稳定处于危险之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/uk-oil-gas-licenses-challenged-in-court-by-environmental-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球股票贸易范围紧密；磅弱：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者在唐纳德·特朗普即将到来的关税方面持续不确定性，全球股票的交易处于紧张的范围内。英国通货膨胀率意外放缓，英镑减弱了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 22:28:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
